text: Jules Rolland (born 24 March 1877, date of death unknown) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics and competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1877 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Valentigney
